    "To denoise the two omics data types, we followed the filtering procedure described in 53 and excluded genes/miRNAs with variance of < 0.02 in the min-max normalized tuning set.",
    "A summary of the omics features before and after preprocessing can be found in Supplementary Table 2.",
    "The min-max normalization process is summarized as follows:",
    "where v ðiÞ and v ðiÞ minmax are the expression data values for feature v in patient i before and after min-max normalization.",
    "v max (v min) is the maximum (minimum) value of v across all patients in the dataset considered."
